title: مسلسل الطائر الرفراف
description: حيث يشتهر فريت ، ابن عائلة ثرية ، بفجوره. لذلك ، اتخذ جده هاليس آغا قرارًا عندما داهمت الشرطة منزله وقرر اتخاذ ابنة عائلة قريبة منها من مسقط رأسه غازي عنتاب كعروس لحفيده.

title: Barbie
description: Barbie suffers a crisis that leads her to question her world and her existence.

title: One Piece
description: In a seafaring world, a young pirate captain sets out with his crew to attain the title of Pirate King, and to discover the mythical treasure known as 'One Piece.'

title: Modern Family
description: Three different but related families face trials and tribulations in their own uniquely comedic ways.

title: Game of Thrones
description: Nine noble families fight for control over the lands of Westeros, while an ancient enemy returns after being dormant for millennia.

title: Indiana Jones and the Dial of Destiny
description: Archaeologist Indiana Jones races against time to retrieve a legendary artifact that can change the course of history.
